		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Im trying to learn how to do graphics and edit them for NES.   I am using a program called FaTILEity.   (other prog's I tried had this problem as well)   When I open up a rom, The Graphics are all out of order.   Is there a way to get these in order as how it would look as if it was on the screen being played?   Thanks!

		

