		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's pretty easy if you just want to modify the tiles themselves, assuming the game uses CHR-ROM.
<br />
<br />But yeah, it can be tricky if you need to modify the actual tile's placement on the screen.  Unless it's text or something else uncompressed, it can be some work to just find where in the ROM the data is.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


