		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Ah, you'll have to find the actual text data inside the ROM, then.  It's usually easy to do if you use a hex editor like hexposure (after you make a .TBL file to identify the font).
<br />
<br />I used that program a while back to translate all of Castlevania 2 and part of Rygar into Spanish.  It was probably pretty bad, because I don't even speak Spanish, heheh.

		

